_sText:
De_Qaria

My second map leaning more toward Competitive play although it still supports
32 player server for those want to use it on a public server. also has a radar and place names done.

Install

Just simply unrar to your cstrike directory example
c:\program files\Steam\steamapps\your user name here\counter-strike source\cstrike

your directory could be slightly different depending on your setup.
